{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"@property"},{"kind":"text","text":" ("},{"kind":"keyword","text":"nonatomic"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"assign"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"getter"},{"kind":"text","text":"="},{"kind":"identifier","text":"isSelected"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"selected"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You should not set the value of this property directly. If the property is set","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to ","type":"text"},{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", the annotation view is displaying a callout.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By default, this property is set to ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" and becomes ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" when the user taps","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the view. Selecting another annotation, whether it is associated with an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" or ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object, deselects any currently","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"selected view.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Setting this property changes the view’s appearance to reflect the new value","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"immediately. If you want the change to be animated, use the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:"},{"text":" method instead.","type":"text"}]}]}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/selected"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/selected","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is currently selected."}],"metadata":{"title":"selected","symbolKind":"property","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"selected","kind":"identifier"}],"fragments":[{"text":"selected","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"remoteSource":{"fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h","url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L212"},"roleHeading":"Instance Property","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(py)selected"},"kind":"symbol","sections":[],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/selected":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/selected","title":"selected","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"selected"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A Boolean value indicating whether the annotation view is currently selected."}],"role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/selected"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","title":"MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects to handle the display.","type":"text"}],"title":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationImage":{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" class is responsible for presenting point-based","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"annotations visually on a map view. Annotation image objects wrap ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIImage"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"objects and may be recycled later and put into a reuse queue that is maintained","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"by the map view.","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationImage"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationImage","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationimage","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotationImage"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setSelected:animated:":{"kind":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:","abstract":[{"text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation.","type":"text"}],"title":"setSelected:animated:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","role":"symbol"}}}